org.docgene.model

Interface XMLParentArticle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.docgene.model.Article, org.docgene.model.HTMLOutput, XMLParent
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    org.docgene.model.AbstractXMLParentArticle, XMLArticle, XMLDisambArticle

    public interface XMLParentArticle
extends org.docgene.model.Article, XMLParent, org.docgene.model.HTMLOutput
    Represents an article which can have children chapters and paragraphs.
